    "user_title": "Apply Safe Coding Principles",
    "value_statement": "AI coding sessions can drift into broad edits, missing context, or unclear handoffs. This skill gives Claude, Codex, and Claude Code practical rules for careful repository reading, minimal edits, and clear guidance.",
    "seo_keywords": [
      "Claude coding principles",
      "Codex safe editing",
      "Claude Code guidelines",
      "diff-aware editing",
      "repository context reading",
